description: Fintie, a quality product within your reach.The Fintie Slim Fit Folio Leather Case offers secure protection for your tablet while adding a range of versatile options. A smart holder is designed to hold your stylus pen, while a soft inner liner and protective corners help safeguard the tablet against scratches and damage. The Fintie Slim Fit Folio Leather Case offers an ideal way to protect your tablet wherever you go. The cover converts to a convenient stand that offer two different angles for viewing, typing, and displaying while an elastic loop offers convenient storage for a pen or stylus.PLEASE NOTE:Colors shown in pictures may slightly differ from actual product due to lighting and color settings.
title: Fintie Folio Case for ASUS MeMO Pad HD 7-inch ME173X Tablet Slim Fit Support Sleep / Wake Function with Stylus Holder - Black
